And I've done some serious study

01:03:48.825 --> 01:03:50.868
over the last few days.

01:03:50.910 --> 01:03:54.539
You know, I've got Connie who is an addiction
research fellow.

01:03:54.581 --> 01:03:57.083
And she's given me so much to read

01:03:57.125 --> 01:03:59.586
<i>that when I couldn't read anymore,</i>

