01:04:54.974 --> 01:04:56.852
And the truth is, we don't know.

01:04:56.893 --> 01:05:00.271
Now, I know you, and I believe you.

01:05:00.313 --> 01:05:03.441
Okay? You look fine to me.

01:05:03.483 --> 01:05:05.736
I've never seen you look this good.

01:05:05.777 --> 01:05:07.320
Never seen you this calm.

01:05:07.362 --> 01:05:09.197
We get about 100 calls a day

01:05:09.239 --> 01:05:12.116
from people trying to get
off drugs and alcohol.

01:05:12.158 --> 01:05:14.411
Ninety calls

01:05:14.452 --> 01:05:16.830
are because of prescription opiates.

01:05:16.872 --> 01:05:18.415
Ninety of them.

01:05:18.456 --> 01:05:21.918
Why do you think that nobody's
stopping the opiate epidemic?

01:05:21.959 --> 01:05:23.670
Let's talk about why it's happening.

01:05:25.255 --> 01:05:28.132
Why it's happening is

01:05:28.174 --> 01:05:31.636
there is no advertising necessary

01:05:33.471 --> 01:05:34.639
<i>for opiates.</i>

01:05:34.681 --> 01:05:36.266
- [Chris] <i> You never see it.
- Never.</i>

01:05:36.307 --> 01:05:39.394
<i>If you stop taking opiates, you get sick.</i>

01:05:40.144 --> 01:05:41.479
<i>You don't have a choice.</i>

01:05:41.521 --> 01:05:43.940
People think slavery ended in 1865,

01:05:43.981 --> 01:05:47.985
it didn't. It's going on right now in 2017.

01:05:48.027 --> 01:05:50.697
Okay? Slavery exists today.

01:05:50.739 --> 01:05:52.657
<i>Okay? If you're on opiates,</i>

01:05:52.699 --> 01:05:54.534
<i>you are a slave.</i>

01:05:54.576 --> 01:05:58.204
<i>You're not controlling that drug, that drug
is controlling you.</i>

01:05:58.246 --> 01:06:01.291
Everything you got. Every goddamn pill.

