[Chris] <i> So, how long does a
shipment this size last?</i>

01:06:04.628 --> 01:06:06.003
How long does it take to sell this?

01:06:06.045 --> 01:06:07.798
- About a month. Yeah.
- Really?

01:06:07.839 --> 01:06:10.049
- 2,500 pounds of kratom in a month?
- Kilos.

01:06:10.091 --> 01:06:12.093
Kilos of kratom in a month.

01:06:12.135 --> 01:06:13.637
[shutter rolls]

